data.name: textBox1.Text
data.value:
In this game you can shoot, load or block with your weapon. Each time you load you get one new piece of ammo, each time you shoot you loose one. The goal is to shoot the enemy when they load, OR gain three pieces of ammo to make your weapon even more powerful. If you shoot the enemy with the maxed out ammo it will be an instant death and you win.
But make sure you shoot first...
